                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article class="card">
                        <img src="~/images/Categories/artsandcraft.jpg" alt="Sample photo">
                        <div class="text">
                            <div class="text">
                                <h3>Arts and Crafts</h3>
                                <p>Meet creative students to widen your creativity and learn how to create different masterpieces</p>
